E4Plus1.uk.description: As Hollyoaks enters its 30th birthday week, longest-serving resident Tony prepares to marry Diane. But secrets threaten to turn his dream day into one nobody will ever forget...

E4Plus1.uk.title: Ramsay's Kitchen Nightmares USA
E4Plus1.uk.description: Mike and Nellie's: In Oakhurst, Gordon Ramsay helps the overwhelmed owner of Mike and Nellie's restaurant, who lost his way when his father and business partner died. (S5 Ep8) [SL]

E4Plus1.uk.title: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: It's another dinner party and It. Is. Serving! Progress is on the menu for some but one couple's authenticity is called into question. Did anyone order tension? (S10 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pygmoelian: After he's snubbed for a Duff beer calendar, Moe goes for plastic surgery and ends up so handsome that he becomes a soap star. (S11 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart to the Future: Bart foresees his adult future as a struggling rock guitarist crashing on Ralph Wiggum's couch, while Lisa becomes President. (S11 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Indecision Amalgamation: Raj has a dating dilemma. Penny can't decide whether to accept a role in a terrible film. Sheldon chooses between two gaming systems. (S7 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Relationship Diremption: Sheldon wonders whether he's wasting his time with his study of string theory. Raj and Emily go on a double date with Howard and Bernadette. (S7 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Virgin Territory: It's a day of disturbing realisations when Mitchell manages to ruin one of Jay's proudest golf moments. Gloria stumbles upon Claire's dangerous little secret. (S3 Ep16)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Modern Family
E4Plus1.uk.description: Leap Day: Cameron's birthday falls on 29 February, and with the celebrations coming but once every four years, there's loads of pressure on Mitchell to get it right. (S3 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Veracity Elasticity: Leonard is upset when he finds out that Penny has been moving his collectables out of Sheldon's old room and into storage behind his back. (S10 Ep7)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Brain Bowl Incubation: Sheldon tries to convince Amy that they should procreate. Raj feels embarrassed about what the new woman in his life does for a living. (S10 Ep8)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Geology Elevation: Sheldon can't contain his jealousy when he hears that his university colleague, Bert the geologist, has won a prestigious fellowship. (S10 Ep9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Property Division Collision: Sheldon, Amy, Leonard and Penny attempt to divide up all their possessions. It doesn't go well. (S10 Ep10)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Therapist: Boyle and Peralta investigate when a psychiatrist reports one of his patients missing. Captain Holt wants to meet Diaz's new girlfriend. (S6 Ep11)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Brooklyn Nine-Nine
E4Plus1.uk.description: Casecation: Peralta and Santiago celebrate their wedding anniversary while standing guard over a comatose drugs baron who was shot and rushed into hospital. (S6 Ep12)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Gone Boy: Bart falls into an old top-secret underground military installation in the woods. (S29 Ep9/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Frink Gets Testy: When Mr Burns panics about the apocalypse and builds a cosmic ark, Professor Frink develops a test to work out who deserves a place on it. (S29 Ep11/21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Relaxation Integration: Amy tries to convince Sheldon that he has a more laid-back side. Raj and Stuart compete to woo Bernadette's new colleague Ruchi. (S11 Ep3)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Explosion Implosion: Howard and Sheldon bond on a trip to the desert to launch a model rocket. Leonard is annoyed when his mother befriends Penny. (S11 Ep4)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Bart After Dark: Bart gets a job at a burlesque theatre. Several residents are keen customers, but others aren't happy to have the showgirls peddling their wares in Springfield. (S8 Ep5/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Simpsoncalifragilisticexpiala (Annoyed Grunt) cious: Supernanny Shary Bobbins comes to the rescue of Marge, who is so stressed that her hair has started to fall out. (S8 Ep13/25)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: The wedding may be over - but the fallout's only just begun. As Tony faces an impossible choice, a life hangs in the balance. And with devastating news spreading, the village is in pieces.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks at 30: Most Explosive...
E4Plus1.uk.description: ...Episodes: Another classic episode. Everyone shelters in The Dog as the violent storm rages outside. But Lily sneaks out into the tempest to check on Romeo when Prince is distracted.

E4Plus1.uk.title: Supercruising: Life at Sea
E4Plus1.uk.description: The crew sailing North Africa and Europe put on an orange party complete with dazzling costumes and a deck-stomping parade, while Caribbean cruisers enjoy a bubbling volcano mud bath. (Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Married at First Sight UK
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series: At another emotionally charged Commitment Ceremony, one couple affirm their love, a bride's behaviour is called out and there's solo sofa surfing... again. (S10 Ep21)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Hannah and Lee both love festivals; will they make sweet music? Mary from Liverpool is looking for a 'straight Paul O'Grady'. And 'edgy librarian' Olivia is on her first ever date. (S7 Ep4)
